divs: Sighting DetailsMy uncle was taking a few pictures across the waterway and did not realize taking any thing other than the view across the water. While taking the picture he says there seemed to be something over to the left side of the field of vision that quickly flew by, but wasn't sure. When the pictues were reviewed later it was noticed this particular one attached had the object in the left side seemingly about 40-50 feet above a 30-40 foot fishing boat. That is all he knows. He wants to know what it is, if it is an actual USO, or UFO, or a bird. Thanks much
trends: There has been one other sighting in Lantana
There were no other sightings in Lantana on or around September 12th 2013
Summary: Was taking a picture across intercontinental waterway and seemed to notice somethign quickly shoot by while taking several pictures across ther waterway. Ome picture caught the object.
